IRS990.Desc: COMPREHENSIVE SYSTEMS, INC. PROVIDES SERVICES AND RESIDENTIAL FACILITIES TO PHYSICALLY AND INTELLECTUALLY DISABLED INDIVIDUALS. APPROXIMATELY 173 INDIVIDUALS WERE SERVED IN THE THE CURRENT YEAR. IN ADDITION TO SERVING INDIVIDUALS LIVING IN THE COMMUNITY, THE ORGANIZATION PROVIDES CARE IN RCF AND ICF/ID CARE FACILITIES FOR THOSE CONSUMERS REQUIRING INTENSIVE TRAINING AND CARE.

ORGANIZATION'S PROCESS TO REVIEW FORM 990. A COPY OF FORM 990 IS MADE AVAILABLE TO THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND DISCUSSED AND APPROVED PRIOR TO FILING.

ENFORCEMENT OF CONFLICTS POLICY. ANY TIME BUSINESS AGREEMENTS ARE MADE BETWEEN INDIVIDUAL BOARD MEMBERS AND COMPREHENSIVE SYSTEMS, INC. WHERE A CONFLICT INTEREST MAY ARISE, THE BOARD WILL BE INFORMED OF SUCH AGREEMENTS AND GIVE APPROVAL. THE MEMBER'S PARTICIPATION IN DISCUSSION WILL BE LIMITED AND HE WILL EXERCISE NO VOTING RIGHTS ON THE ISSUE.

COMPENSATION PROCESS FOR TOP OFFICIAL. THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS, WITH THE ASSISTANCE OF A CONSULTANT, SURVEY SALARIES AT SIMILAR ORGANIZATIONS TO DETERMINE COMPENSATION WHICH IS THEN SUBJECT TO APPROVAL BY THE WHOLE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.

COMPENSATION PROCESS FOR OFFICERS. THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS, WITH THE ASSISTANCE OF A CONSULTANT, SURVEY SALARIES AT SIMILAR ORGANIZATIONS TO DETERMINE COMPENSATION WHICH IS THEN SUBJECT TO APPROVAL BY THE WHOLE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.

GOVERNING DOCUMENTS DISCLOSURE EXPLANATION. GOVERNING DOCUMENTS AND A FINANCIAL SUMMARY MAY BE ACCESSED FROM THE ORGANIZATION'S WEBSITE. FORM 990 IS AVAILABLE ON THE INTERNET AT GUIDESTAR.ORG. ADDITIONAL FINANCIAL INFORMATION IS PROVIDED TO THE GENERAL PUBLIC UPON REQUEST.
